#4503
The Courthouse Lobby~
Dark green marble makes up the floor of this spacious lobby.  With 
whitewashed walls and a dark wooden ceiling, this room contrasts together 
well.  The lobby itself is empty except for the decorative plants set in 
almost random but well thought out places, though they have been arranged to 
leave the center of the room open to view.  A large piece of unpolished 
stone sits in the middle of the floor, and upon closer inspection a short 
engraving can be seen upon its surface.  A massive wooden door to the north 
leads the way into the only courtroom, while to the south, a pair of large 
double doors offers passage outside.  
~
