#4504
Courtroom of Discordia~
This massive chamber has been decorated in a rather spartan manner.  The
floor is covered with a dark green carpet, matching almost perfectly with
the whitewashed walls and dark wooden ceiling.  A series of benches have
been arranged in a half-oval around the north side of the room, though
access has been blocked by the dark wooden bannister built there.  The
northern half of the room has been decorated with a large podium and two
long tables with chairs which have been crafted from the same dark material.
The walls themselves have been decorated with a plethora of paintings of
scenes from the surrounding lands, though the one which dominates the
northern wall is of the Royal Castle of Discordia.  A massive wooden door to
the south leads the way out. 
